description
Dove is not an ordinary bar soap. It is a beauty soap made with Syndet technology that goes beyond cleansing, nourishing the skin as it removes the dirt from everyday life. Dove Delicious Care Shea and Vanilla Soap makes a creamy foam and leaves your skin feeling refreshed. We believe that bathing can be an opportunity for you to take time just for you. That's why we developed the Dove Delicious Care Shea and Vanilla Soap, a soap that brings you our mild cleaning agents and 1/4 moisturizing cream, in addition to a delicate and relaxing scent.

